Package: lsurvROC
Type: Package
Title: Covariate- and Measurement Time-Specific ROC Analysis for Longitudinal Biomarkers with Survival Outcome
Version: 0.0.1
Author: Xiaona Li
Maintainer: Xiaona Li <xiaona0049@gmail.com>
Description: Estimate the biomarker threshold at a specified specificity level along with the corresponding sensitivity using flexible regression models, and construct a covariate- and measurement time-specific ROC curve.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0), quantreg, dplyr, ggplot2, survival
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.2
LazyData: true
